		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_PESANTREN_HELP">
			<Text>+1 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science and +1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith for every 2 [ICON_CITIZEN] Citizens in this City. +25% Religious Pressure from this City. Only Indonesia may build it.</Text>
