		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_PESANTREN_STRATEGY">
			<Text>The Indensian Pesantren replaces the Public School. In addition to the [ICON_RESEARCH] Science yield, it also generates [ICON_PEACE] Faith. Both yields are based on [ICON_CITIZEN] Population, so the Pesantren is most effective in larger cities. It also helps to spread religion faster. Build Pesantrens to help grow and unify your civilization in both religion and research.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_PESANTREN_TEXT">
			<Text>
				Pesantren comes from the Javanese word for "student". A pesantren was formed when a cleric came to reside in an area. Islamic students would come and learn from the house, and eventually their temporary houses would be made into a permanent complex around the teacher's residence.
			</Text>
